name: RazrFi
public_notice: SolRazr (SOLR) has rebranded to RazrFi (SOLR). For more information, please view this announcement on Telegram.

description.en:
What is the project about?
IDOs for: Solana, Arbitrum, Aptos, Sui, Ethereum, Polygon, BSC, Avalanche & all EVM chains 

What makes your project unique?
First AI-driven Multichain Launchpad

History of your project.
A launchpad project formerly known as solrazr rebranding to RazrFi

Whatâ€™s next for your project?
ðŸ”µAI-driven query engine
Ask AI questions in natural language & make informed decisions using AI power!
ðŸ”µAI-driven whitelist for IDOs
AI driven score to auto-whitelist you for IDOs
ðŸ”µAI-driven insights for #IDOs
AI gives a score if wallet should join IDO based on project category, tokenomics & wallet metadata

What can your token be used for?
participate for Initial dex offering and we are committed to add value to our community by innovating & breaking through the monotony that exists in the launchpad space.
